---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<style>
  .card-icon-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light), var(--color-primary-muted));
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover .card-icon-wrapper {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    fill: var(--color-white);
    filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
  }

  .card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>

<section class="section" id="approach">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeading 
      title="Our Approach" 
      subtitle="We embed ourselves within your teams, taking the simplest steps to move forward consistently." 
    />
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-md" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">      
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="card-icon">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10c5.52 0 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm4 12c0 2.21-1.79 4-4 4s-4-1.79-4-4V8c0-1.1.9-2 2-2s2 .9 2 2v5c0 .55-.45 1-1 1s-1-.45-1-1V9h-2v4c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3s3-1.34 3-3V8c0-2.21-1.79-4-4-4S7 5.79 7 8v1H5V8c0-3.86 3.14-7 7-7s7 3.14 7 7v6z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Embedded Expertise</h3>
        <p>Unlike many agencies, we don't simply dictate best practices and leave. We work directly within your teams, gaining first-hand experience of the problems and implementing practical solutions.</p>
        <p>With 50 years of combined experience across diverse industries including BT, BBC, ITV, Just Eat, and VW Bank, we bring proven expertise to your specific challenges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="card-icon">
            <path d="M12 2l-5.5 9h11L12 2zm0 3.84L13.93 9h-3.87L12 5.84zM17.5 13c-2.49 0-4.5 2.01-4.5 4.5s2.01 4.5 4.5 4.5 4.5-2.01 4.5-4.5-2.01-4.5-4.5-4.5zm0 7a2.5 2.5 0 010-5 2.5 2.5 0 010 5zM3 21.5h8v-8H3v8zm2-6h4v4H5v-4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Evolutionary Architecture</h3>
        <p>We help organisations make organisational-scale technical changes, moving towards small, simple, independent, and robust distributed services that are easy to deploy.</p>
        <p>Our approach ensures that technical changes progress in line with business priorities - not so big that they halt throughput, but impactful enough to make a meaningful difference.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
